I"9<p>###How can I send out a CFP to the MSA Community?</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Announce your CFP using the <a href="http://msa.press.jhu.edu/cgi-bin/cfp_view.cgi">MSA CFP page</a> (recommended).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Announce your CFP on the <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/35866051126/?fref=ts">MSA Facebook page</a>; use the hashtag “cfp.”</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Announce your CFP using the list-serv MSA Discuss at
<a href="msa-discuss@jhupress.jhu.edu">msa-discuss@jhupress.jhu.edu</a>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Announce your CFP on Twitter using the <a href="https://twitter.com/msatweet">@msatweet</a> handle and #msa17 #cfp hashtags.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>###How can I find CFPs for MSA 17?</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Look for the hashtag “cfp” on the <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/35866051126/?fref=ts">MSA Facebook page</a>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Look for a CFP on the <a href="http://msa.press.jhu.edu/cgi-bin/cfp_view.cgi">MSA CFP page</a>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Sign up for our mailing list at <a href="http://chaos.press.jhu.edu/mailman/listinfo/msa-discuss">http://chaos.press.jhu.edu/mailman/listinfo/msa-discuss</a>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Look for CFPs on Twitter using the <a href="https://twitter.com/msatweet">@msatweet</a> handle and #msa17 #cfp hashtags.</p>
  </li>
</ol>
